+config A21_AIR_KEEP_WAKE_WORD_AWAKE
+    bool "A21 Air: keep wake-word microphone alive in standby"
+    default y
+    depends on BOARD_TYPE_M5STACK_STACK_CHAN
+    help
+        Keep StackChan usable as a desktop voice satellite by preventing the
+        generic power-save timer from disabling wake-word detection and audio
+        input while the device is idle. The display/app may still manage its
+        own lightweight standby visuals; the microphone stays ready for "大头".
+
